node.text: What’s up everybody, I’ve accepted the #ALLINCHALLENGE. Go to allinchallenge.com/magic-johnson to participate in the auction to play a game of HORSE ahead of sitting courtside with me at a Lakers game. Let's come together & help feed the hungry during this difficult time. @isiahthomas @samuelljackson @jimmykimmel @anthonyanderson @iamsteveharveytv @cedtheentertainer @christucker @chrisrock @officialspikelee I challenge you to be ALL IN!!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Earvin "Magic" Johnson on August 30, 2021. May be an image of 4 people and people standing.

node.text: Happy 10th birthday to my grandson Avery from Pop Pop!!!🎂🎉🎈💙

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Earvin "Magic" Johnson on August 22, 2021 tagging @thecookiej. May be an image of 2 people, people standing, wrist watch and suit.

node.text: Cookie and I enjoyed being back at West Angeles this morning! Bishop Blake was on 🔥🔥🔥 with today’s message “The Battle is not yours but God’s” and today’s reading was from 1 Chronicles 20:15-25.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Earvin "Magic" Johnson on August 20, 2021 tagging @drewbrees. May be an image of 3 people and text.

node.text: What a surprise! Look who I ran into at Dodger Stadium…The NFL’s all-time passing leader, future Hall of Famer and one of the greatest quarterbacks to ever do it, Drew Brees, and his sons.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Earvin "Magic" Johnson on August 20, 2021 tagging @itsnatwilson. May be an image of 2 people, people standing and outdoors.

node.text: Happy birthday to my incredible executive assistant Natalie!! Have a blessed day!
